#: data/io.github.t00m.MiAZ.metainfo.xml.in:9
msgid ""
"Keeping family records, school files, invoices, and administrative paperwork "
"organised is a constant challenge, especially when documents come in from "
"many different countries and institutions."
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.t00m.MiAZ.metainfo.xml.in:10
msgid ""
"MiAZ solves this with a simple, consistent file-naming convention of seven "
"fields: date, country, group, sender, purpose, concept, and recipient. Scan "
"a letter, download an email attachment, drop it into your MiAZ repository, "
"and the app guides you through naming it correctly."
msgstr ""

